{"tid":2054677,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Chen婚後首度登上舞台！　與隊友驚喜現身「口罩遮半臉」賀伯賢奪一位","createTime":"2020-06-07T10:45:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T08:39:30.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"707ad0def20fba7baf0f3cb4a527566187265ad6","tid":2054677,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T10:45:52.000Z","msg":"南韓天團EXO成員Chen先前宣布先有後婚，妻子在4月底也平安生下了女兒，連續震撼彈引爆爭議，讓不少粉絲發表聯合聲明，要求他退出團體。隊友伯賢30日在音樂節目《人氣歌謠》拿下了第一名，EXO成員紛紛驚喜登上安可舞台，而許久未在螢光幕前露臉的他也現身，引起了熱議。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4850/d4850025.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4850%2Fd4850025.jpg&h=46ec10ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Chen時隔近半年在鏡頭前露臉。（圖／翻攝IG）<br />\n<br />\nChen自從公開婚訊後，就幾乎未在公開場合露面過，直到5月隊長Suho的入伍當天，他才與隊友們合體現身，並留下了合照，此次伯賢獲得一位的安可舞台，他也現身力挺，跟KAI、燦烈、世勛一同出現在鏡頭前，義氣十足的舉動也讓不少人大讚EXO「團魂滿滿」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4924/d4924796.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4924%2Fd4924796.jpg&h=f4f97c97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4924/d4924795.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4924%2Fd4924795.jpg&h=7a767b74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Chen現身伯賢的安可舞台。（圖／翻攝推特／lov3toc、《人氣歌謠》）<br />\n<br />\n此前，粉絲曾聯合發起連署要Chen退團，當時SM娛樂為此正面回應聲明：：「本公司作為EXO的經紀公司，不僅要對團體和成員的活動方向負責，對重要事項也一直以成員的意見為優先。」強調跟成員進行長時間討論，因為「EXO全員都經歷過成員離隊的痛苦，向公司表示希望以後一如既往地一起活動」，所以公司尊重成員們的意見，發出聲明告知EXO成員不會有所變動。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3eJ37srHWng\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3eJ37srHWng&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUmyAt0yGCUsyxQooKadsmXE%3D&h=430f0fc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3eJ37srHWng</a><br />\n<br />\n牙陳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ae19ad335809dd7c20f8ee97510d2f99e0fc584","tid":2054677,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T10:49:13.000Z","msg":"吓,佢地冇STAGE都可以一齊上台架?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf903b0b92066601cfbea7afb36cec52315bfa60","tid":2054677,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2ae19ad335809dd7c20f8ee97510d2f99e0fc584","tid":2054677,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T10:49:13.000Z","msg":"吓,佢地冇STAGE都可以一齊上台架?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T10:50:01.000Z","msg":"冇咩問題...經理人都上過台一齊EOCORE啦"},{"pid":"3605dd8725414a29cbe4c799583dbea8804a3d1c","tid":2054677,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T10:54:04.000Z","msg":"我想問啲女係咩意思"},{"pid":"21ec94a7aacf245d0f72331c298141003cb5db2d","tid":2054677,"uid":68678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3605dd8725414a29cbe4c799583dbea8804a3d1c","tid":2054677,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T10:54:04.000Z","msg":"我想問啲女係咩意思"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T11:09:38.000Z","msg":"who lei"},{"pid":"3edfd1c2871d45cee1af3d2af47292bd7cb812fa","tid":2054677,"uid":132174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T11:10:43.000Z","msg":"人逢喜事精神爽"},{"pid":"4f62b6bf73358e53609ee905fbde11771c5883cd","tid":2054677,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21ec94a7aacf245d0f72331c298141003cb5db2d","tid":2054677,"uid":68678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3605dd8725414a29cbe4c799583dbea8804a3d1c","tid":2054677,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T10:54:04.000Z","msg":"我想問啲女係咩意思"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T11:09:38.000Z","msg":"who lei"